quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  3,53,"Joomi amen, min gom…óinii ko nJipin…óaa Kon, men jokkii Nulaa…óo on, Winndu amen e seedii…ďe …ďen."
  3,54,"∆Āe pewji Alla Kadi Fewji. Ko Alla …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude e fewjoo…ďe …ďe."
  3,55,"Tuma Alla winoo: "Hey Iisaa, Min ko mi Hunnoowo ma e ∆Āamtoowo ma faade ta Am, e La…ď…ďinoowo ma immorde e …ďen yeddu…ďe, e Wa…óa …ďen jokku…ďe ma e dow …ďeen yeddu…ďe haa √Ďande Darngal. Refti ko faade ka Am woni ruttorde mon, Mi √Ďaawa hakkunde mon ko luutondirayno-…óon e muu…óum."
  3,56,"Ammaa …ďen yeddu…ďe, Mi Lepta …ďe …óon lepte muuu…óe ka aduna e ka laakara, alanaa…ďe faabotoo…ďe."
  3,57,"Ammaa …ďen gom…óim…ďe …ďe golli golle-mo∆ī∆īe, O timminanay …ďe njo6di ma…ď…ďe ndin. Alla Yi…óaa too√Īoo…ďe …ďen"."
  3,58,"∆äuum …óo, Mi…óen Janngana maa …óum, immorde e Aayeeje e JaŇčtoore √Ďee√Ī…óunde."
  3,59,"Pellet, sifa Iisaa ka Alla, ko sifa Aadama; O Tagii mo immorde e leydi, refti O Daalani mo: "Laato!" o laatii."
  3,60,"Goonga kan ko ko immori ko Joomi maa, wata a laatodo e …ďen sikkitii…ďe."
  3,61,"Kala wennju…óo ma fii makko …ďaawo kon ko ar e maa e ganndal, maaku: "Aree nodden …ďi…ó…ďe amen e …ďi…ó…ďe mo'on, e rew…ďe amen e rew…ďe mo'on, e ko'e amen e ko'e mo'on, refti √Īaago…óen mba…óen kuddi Alla ndin e hoore fenoo…ďe …ďen"."